item.title: Things
item.description: As mentioned in the caption of this website I make music and things! Most of the details of how I'm building what I'm working on can be found on my GitHub page, but here are some of the projects I work on that are cool to see. Interactive Graphics I initially made both of these for use with the Haplet, but I ported them over to javascript using P5.
